sections.Biography:
===Background===
Daena Targaryen was a Queen of the [[House Targaryen|Targaryen]] dynasty and a sister of [[Baelor Targaryen|Baelor the Blessed]], who imprisoned her along their sisters [[Rhaena Targaryen|Rhaena]] and [[Elaena Targaryen|Elaena]] in the [[Maidenvault]] to prevent him from being tempted by carnal thoughts.&lt;ref&gt;[[The Red Keep (Histories &amp; Lore)]]&lt;/ref&gt;

She also became the lover of her cousin, [[Aegon IV Targaryen]]. From their union, [[Daemon Blackfyre]] was born.

===[[Season 1]]===
Daena is mentioned in [[House Targaryen]]'s entry in the book ''[[The Lineages and Histories of the Great Houses of the Seven Kingdoms]]''&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Golden Crown]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
